714277f-a.folder: 69th Street (West) & West End Avenue, Manhattan, NY
714277f-a.text:
West 69th Street, west from West End Ave. to the North (Hudson) River and showing a clearance at the S.W. corner of the first point. Note at the rivers edge, the elevated West Side Vehicular Highway over tracks of the New York Central Railroad. Beyond are the Jersey highlands. View No. 2 of this set emphasizes the aforementioned clearance, West End Ave. being in the foreground. December 19, 1937.

P. L. Sperr
